Description: The unique and rare Okudai Turbo II Covet, originally ZXi Covets, Okudai heavily modified only 5 vehicles into the Okudai Turbo II. Powered by a stage two turbocharged 1.5L Ibishu I4, given modified lowered suspension with Okudai PR01 wheels, and given a special Okudai paint job, the Okudai Turbo II Covets were quick to become street legends.
